nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.persistence.jsonConverter

Interface JsonConverter

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonConverter_Impl

    public interface JsonConverter
    JSON Converter Interface. The JSON Converter Interface is designed to work with the game state of the chap's challenge game. Used by the Persistence_Impl to convert to JSON before saving, or on load.
